Module com.example.demo

Package com.example.demo.view.levels

package com.example.demo.view.levels
Provides classes for managing the visuals and components of different game levels.

This package includes:

  • LevelView - Abstract base class for creating level-specific visuals and UI.
  • LevelOne - Visual configuration and unique elements for Level One.
  • LevelTwo - Visual configuration and unique elements for Level Two.
  • LevelThree - Visual configuration and unique elements for Level Three.
  • LevelFour - Visual configuration and unique elements for Level Four.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    LevelFour
    Represents the visual and UI configuration for Level Four.
    LevelOne
    Represents the visual and UI configuration for Level One, including unique elements like tutorial messages.
    LevelThree
    Represents the visual and UI configuration for Level Three.
    LevelTwo
    Represents the visual and UI configuration for Level Two.
    LevelView
    Abstract base class for defining visuals and UI for game levels.
